{"tid":1634640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国有四大国有銀行，俗稱四大行","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:30:49.000Z","uid":36775,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"368d369880a9abc6291a80af500e125a85005a05","tid":1634640,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"國有銀行係由國家控制銀行，即係國企。而中国国有銀行有四間，俗稱四大行<br />\n1. 中国建設銀行<br />\n2. 中国銀行(香港)<br />\n3. 中国工商銀行<br />\n4. 中国農業銀行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nopt6bq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNopt6bq.png&h=96b17b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住喇，上海商業銀行係台資，唔係中国咖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f1c042479b0086ecb9a1b41d46758022088ee5","tid":1634640,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新口號：和勇相連 絕不割蓆！</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b36d96adc2f93407f235e7bb14aa5cd2f58e2a","tid":1634640,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"應該開係財經台<br />\n開錯台，sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491729b1c3b8f4f9547f90fd275c99da7f561260","tid":1634640,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"全民㩒爆atm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4116acabcdc61cd6c2cc0645202286226ca062a